        "latin": "Wa i\u017c\u0101 q\u012bla lahum ta\u2018\u0101lau yastagfir lakum ras\u016blull\u0101hi lawwau ru'\u016bsahum wa ra'aitahum ya\u1e63udd\u016bna wa hum mustakbir\u016bn(a).",
